('paladin-of-white-dragon', 'Paladin of White Dragon', 'Monster', 'You can Ritual Summon this card with "White Dragon Ritual". At the start of the Damage Step, if this card attacks a face-down Defense Position monster: Destroy that face-down monster. You can Tribute this card; Special Summon 1 "Blue-Eyes White Dragon" from your hand or Deck, but "Blue-Eyes White Dragons" cannot attack for the rest of this turn.', 'official', 'mixed', 'verified', timezone('utc', now()), 'Merged from local CSV and verified external card data.', 18, true, '73398797', null, 'LIGHT', 4, null, null, ARRAY[]::text[], null, 1900, 1200, null, 'Ritual Effect Monster', 'Dragon', ARRAY['Ritual', 'Effect']::text[], null, false, ARRAY[]::text[], null, null, ARRAY['Blue-Eyes White Dragon']::text[], ARRAY[]::text[], ARRAY[]::text[], ARRAY['Summon', 'Trigger', 'Ignition']::text[], 'partial', null),
