('underworld-circle', 'Underworld Circle', 'Spell', 'Activate this card if both players have 5 or more monsters in their GYs; destroy as many monsters on the field as possible, then each player banishes (face-down) all monsters from their Deck, then you can Special Summon 1 Normal Monster from your GY. Once per turn, during the Standby Phase: Activate this effect; each player can Special Summon 1 monster from their GY, ignoring its Summoning conditions, but banish it when it leaves the field. You can only activate 1 "Underworld Circle" per Duel.', 'anime', 'mixed', 'verified', timezone('utc', now()), 'Backfilled from Yu-Gi-Oh Wiki/Fandom.', 24, true, '73443672', null, 'WATER', 1, null, null, ARRAY[]::text[], null, 100, 100, 'Continuous', 'Aqua / Effect', 'Aqua', ARRAY['Effect']::text[], 'Continuous', false, ARRAY[]::text[], null, null, ARRAY[]::text[], ARRAY[]::text[], ARRAY[]::text[], ARRAY[]::text[], 'unsupported', 'Spell effect is not implemented yet.'),
